title: How to Get Re-Inspired When You're In a Funk
description: What do you do when you have ZERO inspiration and like you're just stuck in a funk? Ugh. So frustrating. In this episode, Jordan covers her 7 go-to steps that have helped her get re-inspired when she's in a funk or creative rut. Tune in to learn and apply these to your life and work, too!
